         <abstract id="aspace_e5b81deb6b94a25b6bf719c4cf19a7d3">The records consist of correspondence, applications for licensing and funding, agreements, and meeting minutes documenting the Yale New Haven Educational Corporation (YNHEC) and its unsuccessful attempt to establish an education television station in New Haven, Connecticut.</abstract>
